casebody.data:
Friday, December 11, 1998

MOTION DOCKET

98-206. Sasaki v. McKinnon.

Cuyahoga App. No. 71941. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellants’ motion to remand appeal to the trial court,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to remand appeal to the trial court be, and hereby is, denied.

Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., dissent.
